com.esri.mo2.map.elt
Class BaseGroupElement

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.esri.mo2.map.elt.BaseElement
        |
        +--com.esri.mo2.map.elt.BaseGroupElement
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable, Data, Element, GroupElement, Identifiable, MapData, Spatial
public class BaseGroupElement
extends BaseElement
implements GroupElement

This is the base class for GroupElement. It implements the GroupElement interface. Eventhough it's named as BaseGroupElement, it has a no-op constructor and can be instantiated. The group element is always sitting on the bottom of all the elements it contains when it's added to the Layout
